[13.203842, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “CycloneDX, downloadable, every input with its content hash.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ open https://glaas.ai — paste the hash, click Audit (AI-BOM)\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  [NET] fallback: cast/glaas-aibom.cast\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[16.218299, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Now: you don't have to trust me. Rebuild it yourself from the hash alone.”\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;33m  “First, what it WOULD do — the recorded plan. This is instant.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
