[34.221906, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Same hash. Bit for bit. That is what dereferenceable means.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[34.221974, "o", "\r\n"]
[37.23364, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36mACT 2 — THE REVEAL   (~30 sec)   The kicker.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.233758, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Everything you just watched came from typing this in front of my”\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;33m  “training command. No config. No instrumentation. No pipeline file.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.233784, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;37m  $ roar run python train.py\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[37.234073, "o", "\r\n"]
[40.244815, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “That's it. That's the whole integration. It was free.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[40.244991, "o", "\r\n"]
[43.252067, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;36mACT 3 — PAYOFF   (~2 min)   The record surfaces what I never declared.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[43.252237, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “One human act. I marked the raw dataset as containing personal data.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ roar tag show data/raw.csv\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[43.558322, "o", "Tags on data/raw.csv:\r\n  contains_pii=present\r\n"]
[43.583989, "o", "\r\n"]
[46.591712, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “I never said anything about the other files. Watch where it went.”\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ python taint.py\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[47.044462, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[1mBLAST RADIUS\u001b[0m   contains_pii   ·   session 2\r\n\r\n  \u001b[2m@1\u001b[0m generate\r\n"]
[47.226678, "o", "       \u001b[1;31m●\u001b[0m data/raw.csv              \u001b[1;31mcontains_pii=present    \u001b[0m\u001b[2m← tagged here\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[47.678285, "o", "  \u001b[2m@2\u001b[0m preprocess\r\n"]
[47.860326, "o", "       \u001b[1;31m●\u001b[0m data/test.csv             \u001b[1;31mcontains_pii=present    \u001b[0m\u001b[2minherited\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[48.311443, "o", "       \u001b[1;31m●\u001b[0m data/train.csv            \u001b[1;31mcontains_pii=present    \u001b[0m\u001b[2minherited\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[48.765284, "o", "  \u001b[2m@3\u001b[0m train\r\n"]
[48.95066, "o", "       \u001b[1;31m●\u001b[0m model.pkl                 \u001b[1;31mcontains_pii=present    \u001b[0m\u001b[2minherited\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[49.405801, "o", "  \u001b[2m@4\u001b[0m evaluate\r\n"]
[49.59095, "o", "       \u001b[1;31m●\u001b[0m metrics.json              \u001b[1;31mcontains_pii=present    \u001b[0m\u001b[2minherited\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[50.044365, "o", "\r\n  \u001b[1;31m\u001b[1m5 of 5 artifacts carry contains_pii\u001b[0m\r\n  \u001b[2mnobody declared this. it followed the data.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[50.055804, "o", "\r\n"]
[53.066064, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “Five artifacts. One declaration. The tag followed the data, not a config.”\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[0;33m  “That's a blast radius — and it's the answer to 'which models are affected?'”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[53.066201, "o", "\r\n"]
[56.072878, "o", "\u001b[0;33m  “And it's not a guess. Ask the model why it's tainted, and it shows its work.”\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[56.073218, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1;32m$ roar tag why contains_pii model.pkl\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[56.384678, "o", "Why does model.pkl have contains_pii?\r\n  model.pkl: contains_pii=present — inherited via job dde4363a\r\n      └─ train.csv: contains_pii=present — inherited via job 9119c6bc\r\n          └─ raw.csv: contains_pii=present — user `roar run --add-tag` in job 7a3e8225 (session-scoped)\r\n      └─ test.csv: contains_pii=present — inherited via job 9119c6bc\r\n          └─ raw.csv: contains_pii=present — user `roar run --add-tag` in job 7a3e8225 (session-scoped)\r\n"]
[56.411406, "o", "\r\n"]
